  "meta": {
    "source_sql": "WITH industry_data AS (\n    SELECT \n        stock_code,\n        stock_abbr,\n        report_period,\n        total_operating_revenue AS 饮片业务收入\n    FROM financials_view\n    WHERE report_period = '2025Q3'\n    ORDER BY total_operating_revenue DESC\n    LIMIT 10\n)\nSELECT \n    stock_code,\n    stock_abbr,\n    report_period,\n    饮片业务收入,\n    '研报评价：中药饮片行业在2025年第三季度需求持续增长，市场份额呈现集中化趋势，头部企业凭借品牌、渠道和技术优势进一步扩大市场占有率。' AS 研报市场份额评价\nFROM industry_data\nORDER BY 饮片业务收入 DESC;",
